description:
Danny recaps this week's The Real Housewives of New York, which featured the women in Harlem, the introduction of Bershan Shaw, and Ramona's vertigo acting up. After the recap, Danny sits down with legendary voice actor Billy West, who voices BUGS BUNNY in Space Jam, Doug in Doug, the red M&M, BOTH Ren and Stimpy in Ren and Stimpy, and SO many other iconic characters. They discuss working while on the autism spectrum, Futurama, Looney Tunes, and SO much more.


Billy West Interview: 28:50ish
